    <content>
      <Value><![CDATA[{
  "layout": {
    "Umbraco.BlockList": [
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/d6f82beda9154c5492e5eeb70e831980"
      },
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/99ca965ef19c4a229de38f14e112fae2"
      },
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/f1963991341344a9b8c3a8a2eec4061b"
      },
      {
        "contentUdi": "umb://element/2f7fe5d6c97a47988da51148aed8a07d"
      }
    ]
  },
  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "9c273b63-8c63-40b8-88ab-614cec2c97d1",
      "udi": "umb://element/d6f82beda9154c5492e5eeb70e831980",
      "richText": "<h2><span class=\"-blue-text\"><strong>Step 1 - ICR calculation</strong></span></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Enter the loan amount needed for this application, including any product fees to be added to the loan</li>\n<li>Enter the estimated or current monthly rental income</li>\n<li>Choose either a 1-4 year or 5 year fixed term.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Find our Buy to Let <strong><a href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/2daf054a86884de68d49c0ed54780cf2}?ProductType=Buy+to+Let&amp;ProductTerm=null&amp;ProductCategory=null&amp;ProductLTV=null&amp;InterestOnly=false\" title=\"New Business Products\" data-anchor=\"?ProductType=Buy+to+Let&amp;ProductTerm=null&amp;ProductCategory=null&amp;ProductLTV=null&amp;InterestOnly=false\">products here</a></strong>.</p>\n<h2><span class=\"-blue-text\"><strong>Step 2 - Top Slicing calculation </strong></span></h2>\n<p>To see what your client could borrow on a Buy to Let Top Slicing mortgage, we need more information.</p>\n<p><strong>Please expand each item below for more information on what to include for our assessment:</strong></p>"
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "94dff9fd-1c74-4e83-8a0b-e432ba231b33",
      "udi": "umb://element/99ca965ef19c4a229de38f14e112fae2",
      "title": "Applicant information and finances",
      "fAQs": {
        "layout": {
          "Umbraco.BlockList": [
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/85b758ab0a684f3d80822c661fb12be1"
            },
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/880eb2eeff6e46f3a246f264ebaf7ae6"
            },
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/58c7e801221c48b4a73bbe891c6be9b7"
            },
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/405452dfcfc24b16aacaae2a9d715f84"
            }
          ]
        },
        "contentData": [
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/85b758ab0a684f3d80822c661fb12be1",
            "question": "Number of adults",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/ebae742e80264ac08658ef773d1c07b7"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/ebae742e80264ac08658ef773d1c07b7",
                  "answer": "<p>Enter the number of applicants and any other adults who are financially dependent upon the applicants. All applicants must live at the same residential address and at least one must be a homeowner.</p>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          },
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/880eb2eeff6e46f3a246f264ebaf7ae6",
            "question": "Number of children",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/4b399f4afdf541fcb840f8b42bdaec6f"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/4b399f4afdf541fcb840f8b42bdaec6f",
                  "answer": "<p>Enter the number of children under the age of 18. Exclude any children who do not live with the applicants.</p>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          },
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/58c7e801221c48b4a73bbe891c6be9b7",
            "question": "Annual income (£)",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/851d39b2054541f9a314aae7ebe4edc5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/851d39b2054541f9a314aae7ebe4edc5",
                  "answer": "<p><strong><span class=\"-blue-text\">The minimum household income for a Top Slicing mortgage is £40,000</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Employed client:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Include their annual gross basic salary including any occupational pension (the amount before tax and national insurance deductions)</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">We accept 50% of regular additional (non-guaranteed) income such as; overtime, commission and annual or bi-annual bonuses</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Our underwriters may reduce the amount of reliance on this income at their discretion.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Self employed client:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Your client’s business must have been trading for a minimum of three years</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">We’ll assess the last two years’ income and will take an average of the last two years’ SA302’s. If the SA302’s show a decline in income we’ll use the lowest latest year’s figure in isolation</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">For directors with a 25% or greater shareholding we’ll use the latest year’s director’s salary, plus an average of the last 2 years’ dividends.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Retirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">If your client’s retirement is less than 10 years away, and the requested term will extend into retirement, include either their anticipated retirement income or their current income if lower.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>If your client also receives:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\"><strong>Child maintenance</strong> - include the annual amount received. The associated children should be entered in the ‘Number of children’ field as financial dependants. Child maintenance cannot be the only form of income on an application</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\"><strong>Foster income</strong> - average their last two years' earned UK taxable income, or use their most recent year's income if it’s lower than the average. Foster children must be included in the ‘Number of children’ field as financial dependants.</span></li>\n</ul>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          },
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/405452dfcfc24b16aacaae2a9d715f84",
            "question": "Monthly outgoings",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/489943c4878e4e62b4698ef1a1af5723"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/489943c4878e4e62b4698ef1a1af5723",
                  "answer": "<p>Enter the total amount (combined for joint applicants) your client will continue to pay each month for committed outgoings.</p>\n<p><strong>Include:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Car finance and personal loans</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Student loans</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Any loans or credit where your client is acting as a guarantor</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Second or subsequent charges secured on your client's property</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Hire purchase commitments</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Overdraft interest calculated at 2% of the current overdraft balance</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Credit card/store card/catalogue debts calculated at 3% of the current outstanding balance</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Childcare costs/child maintenance/alimony</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">School fees</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets list-ticks\">Interest costs on any non Buy to Let mortgages your client holds, calculated at 9.04% of the approximate balance at completion. Please don’t include their current residential mortgage.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Exclude:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Living expenses (e.g. food, utility bills, clothes, petrol)</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Subscriptions to leisure activities (e.g. gym or golf club membership)</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Ground rent, lease payments or maintenance for other properties</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Pension contributions</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Commitments, payments or rent that will cease if this mortgage completes</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Monthly payments for other mortgages, even if they will continue after completion.</span></li>\n</ul>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          }
        ],
        "settingsData": []
      }
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "94dff9fd-1c74-4e83-8a0b-e432ba231b33",
      "udi": "umb://element/f1963991341344a9b8c3a8a2eec4061b",
      "title": "Residential mortgage details",
      "fAQs": {
        "layout": {
          "Umbraco.BlockList": [
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/e2e304b3d60d4f50a00f687251f2b1bc"
            }
          ]
        },
        "contentData": [
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/e2e304b3d60d4f50a00f687251f2b1bc",
            "question": "Outstanding balance (£)",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/77ea34da092c4abd876e0083f79887b0"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/77ea34da092c4abd876e0083f79887b0",
                  "answer": "<p>If applicant 1 or 2 has an outstanding residential mortgage, please enter the outstanding balance and monthly repayment.</p>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          }
        ],
        "settingsData": []
      }
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "94dff9fd-1c74-4e83-8a0b-e432ba231b33",
      "udi": "umb://element/2f7fe5d6c97a47988da51148aed8a07d",
      "title": "Existing Buy to Let properties",
      "fAQs": {
        "layout": {
          "Umbraco.BlockList": [
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/b07d9ce3853849ebb3f5fa72a76151ca"
            },
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/e5767caacdf345c4854c02b7cd39a333"
            },
            {
              "contentUdi": "umb://element/cb7a4664d4994c53ba4af5557a114dfb"
            }
          ]
        },
        "contentData": [
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/e5767caacdf345c4854c02b7cd39a333",
            "question": "Total balance of all Buy to Let properties (£)",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/2347de66bcb74dc284359f2a694d24d4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/2347de66bcb74dc284359f2a694d24d4",
                  "answer": "<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Enter the balance of all Buy to Let mortgages excluding this application. This must include any that are in joint names, and all applications in progress</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Include any that are in the name of a limited company which your client is a director of.</span></li>\n</ul>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          },
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/cb7a4664d4994c53ba4af5557a114dfb",
            "question": "Total monthly rental income (£)",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/94e1729c0e644591bc98f9196a1a315b"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/94e1729c0e644591bc98f9196a1a315b",
                  "answer": "<ul>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Enter the rental income achieved for all Buy to Let properties, excluding this application</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"list-bullets\">Please don't include any rental income already accounted for in your client’s annual income.</span></li>\n</ul>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          },
          {
            "contentTypeKey": "cc37be6c-af82-4a8f-bcfe-5dc50d675c4f",
            "udi": "umb://element/b07d9ce3853849ebb3f5fa72a76151ca",
            "question": "Buy to Let borrowing",
            "answer": {
              "layout": {
                "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                  {
                    "contentUdi": "umb://element/ae377828a93b4080bfd181c722a3edb2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "contentData": [
                {
                  "contentTypeKey": "dba6735d-7dc0-4fe4-b679-bb35d308181a",
                  "udi": "umb://element/ae377828a93b4080bfd181c722a3edb2",
                  "answer": "<p>We need to make sure any Buy to Let borrowing is self financing. If it isn’t, any shortfall will be classified as an outgoing.</p>"
                }
              ],
              "settingsData": []
            }
          }
        ],
        "settingsData": []
      }
    }
  ],
  "settingsData": []
}]]></Value>
